      • initialize

        public void initialize(java.net.URL url,
                       java.util.ResourceBundle resourceBundle)
        This method is responsible for gathering the names of the top 5 users (by score) from the AccountManager. These names will be displayed in the text fields provided on the page. If the user is an admin, the class name will be the ID corresponding to the admin, which can differ from that of a teacher.
        Specified by:
        initialize in interface javafx.fxml.Initializable
